<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>WastedToken Mint — Collectible Physical Challenge Coins</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --bg-dark: #0a0a0f;
    --bg-card: #12121a;
    --gold: #d4a853;
    --gold-light: #f0d48a;
    --bronze: #b87333;
